      "path": "src/app/privacy-policy/page.tsx",
      "content": "export default function PrivacyPage() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto p-6 text-gray-800\">\n      <h1 className=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Privacy Policy</h1>\n      \n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        At Mirelle Inspo (mirelleinspo.com), we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring \n        transparency about how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information. This Privacy \n        Policy explains our data practices and your rights regarding your information.\n      </p>\n\n      <p className=\"mb-6 text-sm italic text-gray-600\">\n        <strong>Effective Date:</strong> October 6, 2025\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">1. Information We Collect</h2>\n      \n      <h3 className=\"text-lg font-semibold mt-4 mb-2\">1.1 Information You Provide</h3>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide when you:\n      </p>\n      <ul className=\"list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-1\">\n        <li>Subscribe to our newsletter (email address, name)</li>\n        <li>Submit comments or feedback (name, email address, comment content)</li>\n        <li>Contact us via email or contact forms (name, email address, message content)</li>\n        <li>Participate in surveys or promotions (information you choose to provide)</li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <h3 className=\"text-lg font-semibold mt-4 mb-2\">1.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        When you visit our website, we automatically collect certain technical information through \n        cookies and similar tracking technologies, including:\n      </p>\n      <ul className=\"list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-1\">\n        <li>IP address and approximate geographic location</li>\n        <li>Browser type, version, and language settings</li>\n        <li>Device information (type, operating system, screen resolution)</li>\n        <li>Pages visited, time spent on pages, and navigation patterns</li>\n        <li>Referring website or source that directed you to our site</li>\n        <li>Date and time of visits</li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        We use the collected information for the following purposes:\n      </p>\n      <ul className=\"list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-1\">\n        <li><strong>Website Operation:</strong> To provide, maintain, and improve our website functionality</li>\n        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> To respond to your inquiries, comments, and support requests</li>\n        <li><strong>Newsletter:</strong> To send you email updates, blog posts, and nail care tips (with your consent)</li>\n        <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> To analyze website traffic, user behavior, and content performance</li>\n        <li><strong>Personalization:</strong> To customize content and recommendations based on your interests</li>\n        <li><strong>Advertising:</strong> To display relevant advertisements through third-party ad networks</li>\n        <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> To comply with legal obligations and protect our rights</li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        Mirelle Inspo uses cookies, web beacons, and similar tracking technologies to enhance your \n        browsing experience and collect usage data. Cookies are small text files stored on your device \n        that help us recognize your browser and remember your preferences.\n      </p>\n\n      <h3 className=\"text-lg font-semibold mt-4 mb-2\">3.1 Types of Cookies We Use</h3>\n      <ul className=\"list-disc ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2\">\n        <li>\n          <strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for website functionality, including navigation \n          and access to secure areas\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how visitors interact with our website \n          (e.g., Google Analytics)\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <strong>Advertising Cookies:</strong> Used by third-party ad networks to display relevant ads \n          and measure ad campaign effectiveness\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <strong>Functionality Cookies:</strong> Remember your preferences and settings for a personalized \n          experience\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n\n      <h3 className=\"text-lg font-semibold mt-4 mb-2\">3.2 Managing Cookies</h3>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        You can control and manage cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to \n        refuse or delete cookies. Please note that disabling cookies may affect website functionality \n        and your user experience. To opt out of interest-based advertising, visit the Digital Advertising \n        Alliance opt-out page or the Network Advertising Initiative opt-out page.\n      </p>\n\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2\">4. Third-Party Services and Data Sharing</h2>\n      \n      <h3 className=\"text-lg font-semibold mt-4 mb-2\">4.1 Google AdSense</h3>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        We use Google AdSense to display advertisements on our website. Google AdSense uses cookies and \n        similar technologies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our website and other websites. \n        Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your browsing \n        history across different sites.\n      </p>\n      <p className=\"mb-4\">\n        You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting{\" \"}\n        <a \n          href=\"https://www.google.com/settings/ads\" \n          target=\"_blank\" \n          rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n          className=\"text-blue-600 underline hover:text-blue-800\"\n        >\n          Google 